 20:10:54'),(741,112,23,'All good.','2009-03-29 20:12:02','2009-03-29 20:12:02'),(742,152,23,'Some of the sheep ruts are becoming too deep and narrow for pedals, though there are plenty of lines to choose from so not a problem.','2009-03-29 20:15:08','2009-03-29 20:15:08'),(743,143,23,'Stick to the beaten track on the upper sections, as the long grass on either side hides plenty of bumps and dips. The bottom 0.3km has been recently trimmed, with lots of dry gorse on the track.','2009-03-29 20:17:06','2009-03-29 20:17:06'),(744,116,23,'In fine condition â€“ firm and dry.','2009-03-29 20:22:15','2009-03-29 20:22:15'),(745,102,23,'Valley floor section is in good condition.  The two unbridged creek crossings north of [[track:143]] are easily ridable.','2009-03-29 20:31:07','2009-03-29 20:31:07'),(746,279,23,'In fine condition. Firm and smooth gravel surface.','2009-03-31 20:54:21','2009-03-31 20:54:21'),(747,228,92,'Access to the new downhill (stage 4) is getting quite potted. Generally tracks in that area are dusty, steep and fast.','2009-04-04 14:59:58','2009-04-04 14:59:58'),(748,284,23,'Generally in good condition, apart from a few ruts and exposed rocky bits in the middle section.','2009-04-05 12:51:45','2009-04-05 12:51:45'),(749,288,23,'Looks fine â€“ smooth grass and dirt surface in good condition.','2009-04-05 12:57:03','2009-04-05 12:57:03'),(750,289,23,'Compacted dirt and exposed bedrock, polished by many quad bikes, with an occasional patch of loose gravel.','2009-04-05 12:59:28','2009-04-05 12:59:28'),(751,291,23,'There\'s some glass and other debris swept off State Highway 1 onto the path in a couple of places, but otherwise all good.','2009-04-05 20:40:09','2009-04-05 20:40:09'),(752,292,23,'The middle section is being upgraded, so the surface is a bit rougher than the rest - though hardly noticeable.','2009-04-05 20:41:35','2009-04-05 20:41:35'),(753,290,23,'The grassy parts are well trimmed. There are a few moderate ruts on the steeper sections, though 