 Everything else is in fine condition.','2010-01-01 10:26:32','2010-01-01 10:26:32'),(1186,80,23,'In excellent condition â€“ dry and firm throughout.','2010-01-01 10:28:58','2010-01-01 10:28:58'),(1187,74,23,'Some 0.25km below the intersection with [[track:77]] a drain across the track has become a sharp V-shape.  Could be rather awkward if hit at just the right speed.','2010-01-01 10:33:25','2010-01-01 10:33:25'),(1188,75,23,'In great condition.  There\'s still a low hanging tree or two to watch out for.','2010-01-01 10:44:23','2010-01-01 10:44:23'),(1189,76,23,'Really dry, with a scattering of loose gravel on a hard base.','2010-01-01 10:49:37','2010-01-01 10:49:37'),(1190,739,23,'The top half of the track has a firm gravel base. The rest can be ridden, though has a somewhat less manicured surface.','2010-01-01 11:42:05','2010-01-01 11:42:05'),(1191,738,23,'Still under construction, so the track surface is a bit rough in places and some of the drops are not yet complete.  Ridable throughout, though with some effort.','2010-01-01 11:45:31','2010-01-01 11:45:31'),(1192,77,23,'[[track:738]] is ridable throughout, though it is still under construction.','2010-01-01 11:48:09','2010-01-01 11:48:09'),(1193,613,23,'The build is progressing well. Currently there\'s about 400m of benched, though not quite finished, track at the top and a further 250m of benching at the bottom end.','2010-01-01 12:04:39','2010-01-01 12:04:39'),(1194,741,23,'The track is in great condition. The surface looks to have been recently upgraded, with some sections re-cut to eliminate steps and even out the gradient.','2010-01-02 15:09:06','2010-01-02 15:09:06'),(1195,742,23,'Reasonably dry and firm, though the steeper sections look like they would be a challenge when wet.','2010-01-02 15:10:02','2010-01-02 15:10:13'),(1196,743,23,'At just above the halfway point there\'s a large tree across the track at head height â€“ remember to duck.','2010-01-02 15:11:46','2010-01-02 15:11:46'),(1197,744,23,'Generally in good condition, dry and firm throughout.','2010-01-02 15:13:02','2010-01-02 15:13:02'),(1198,83,23,'Section between [[track:741]] and [[track:742]] is dry and firm, with lots of exposed tree roots, occasional ruts, and a covering of crunchy leaves.','2010-01-02 15:16:00','2010-01-02 15:16:00'),(1199,82,23,'The short section between [[track:743]] and [[track:744]] is dry, with lots of exposed tree roots, a few ruts, and plenty of crunchy leaves.  A couple of stepped sections are developing bypasses that look steep but ridable.','2010-01-02 15:18:28','2010-01-02 15:18:28'),(1200,506,139,'This track has been weed wacked and is now clear once more of the spring growth - we need more people to ride it to keep the growth down so get up there people ;)','2010-01-02 23:43:08','2010-01-02 23:43:08'),(1201,507,139,'This track is in desperate need of some weed wacking after the spring growth - it is rideable but very overgrown in patches!','2010-01-02 23:44:00','2010-01-02 23:44:00'),(1202,508,139,'This track was cleared in the last couple of days of spring growth and is now rideable again - get back up there people and enjoy - riding helps keep the weeds down ;)','2010-01-02 23:45:08','2010-01-02 23:45:08'),(1203,509,139,'We have now compeleted the upgrade on this trail, joining it to the ends of Matai and Rimu to make a great flowing exit out of either trails.  Recently cleared of spring growth, it is well worth a visit.','2010-01-02 23:46:15','2010-01-02 23:46:15'),(1204,159,23,'Section between [[track:779]] and [[track:780]] is in fine condition, with the usual loose rocky surface.','2010-01-03 10:56:54','2010-01-03 10:56:54'),(1205,779,23,'The track is currently being upgraded, with lots of new steps having been built.','2010-01-03 10:58:14','2010-01-03 10:58:14'),(1207,780,23,'Some of the many steps are in poor condition.  Perhaps they\'ll get an upgrade like that currently nearing completion on [[track:779]]?','2010-01-03 11:04:20','2010-01-03 11:04:20'),(120